40:52.375 --> 40:54.958
<i>Lakers on the run.</i>
<i>Magic, beautiful pass</i>
<i>to Nixon! Oh my!</i>

40:55.041 --> 40:57.166
<i>Oh, showtime, folks!</i>

40:57.250 --> 40:59.541
<i>To Cooper. Slam dunk!</i>
<i>Just gorgeous.</i>

40:59.625 --> 41:01.958
<i>Remarkable passing</i>
<i>by the Lakers.</i>

41:02.041 --> 41:03.625
<i>Ha, ha!</i>

41:05.583 --> 41:08.708
<i>And the Lakers ran away</i>
<i>with this conference semi,</i>

41:08.791 --> 41:09.833
<i>a rematch with Seattle</i>

41:09.916 --> 41:11.708
<i>the only thing</i>
<i>standing in their way</i>

41:11.791 --> 41:13.500
for a trip to the NBA finals.

41:29.333 --> 41:31.166
Love you.

